{"tid":1562002,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"祖國館山市斷水停電，軍隊開放浴室供市民免費使用。","createTime":"2019-09-12T00:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T16:11:47.000Z","uid":43041,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"18692b56063868c9817ea061532aeaddc5307a0a","tid":1562002,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evFdR3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevFdR3D.jpg&h=7f08671a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n千葉県館山市の広い範囲で断水や停電が続いていることから、海上自衛隊館山航空基地では、ふだん隊員たちが使っている浴室を無料で開放しています。<br />\n<br />\n開放しているのは基地内にある隊員たちがふだん使っている大浴室で、男性用がおよそ４０人、女性用がおよそ８０人同時に利用できます。<br />\n<br />\n利用時間は午後１時から午後７時までで、基地内の施設で給水や携帯電話などの充電、洗濯もできるということです。"},{"pid":"bb9cd6f324143ba2a3149b3b3a1db81366405d59","tid":1562002,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:03:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3839163349917a11f03fab8093b87a697e6c8b25","tid":1562002,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d703484b9f31620a2bdcac04db0ea688d6ea70e6","tid":1562002,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00: